Structs/Scatter.html.name: Scatter
Structs/Scatter.html.abstract: The scatter trace type encompasses line charts, scatter charts, text charts, and bubble charts.

Structs/ScatterGL.html.name: ScatterGL
Structs/ScatterGL.html.abstract: The data visualized as scatter point or lines is set in x and y using the WebGL plotting engine.

Structs/Bar.html.name: Bar

Structs/Sunburst.html.name: Sunburst
Structs/Sunburst.html.abstract: Visualize hierarchal data spanning outward radially from root to leaves.

Structs/Sankey.html.name: Sankey
Structs/Sankey.html.abstract: Sankey plots for network flow data analysis.

Structs/Treemap.html.name: Treemap
Structs/Treemap.html.abstract: Visualize hierarchal data from leaves (and/or outer branches) towards root with rectangles.
